    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong><em>Welcome to my new blog!</em></strong></p><a id="more"></a><p>Recently, I created a new blog based on <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>. I have browsed all 320 themes on hexo.io, but I don’t like any of them. So I created a new one on my own - <a href="https://github.com/MrWillCom/hexo-theme-cupertino">Cupertino</a>.</p><p><img src="/img/000001.png" alt="A screen shot of theme Cupertino"></p><p><a href="https://github.com/MrWillCom/hexo-theme-cupertino">This theme</a> is based on Cupertino Design with light border and translucent and acrylic background on navigation bar, supports dark appearance and powerful footer.</p><p>This blog is generated automatically by <a href="https://github.com/MrWillCom/MrWillCom.github.io/blob/master/.github/workflows/blog-builder.yml">an action</a> when I push to the repository, written by <a href="https://github.com/aeilot">@aeilot</a> and I improved it.</p>]]></content>
    
    
